    <string name="info_about_body1">OpenVibble 是 Claude Desktop Buddy 硬件桌搭的陪伴 App。</string>
    <string name="info_about_body2">顶部显示 BLE 状态，中部显示像素宠物，底部 A/B 模拟实体按键。</string>
    <string name="info_about_body3">收到 Claude Desktop 的权限请求后，A=允许 / B=拒绝。</string>
    <string name="info_about_body4">源码 MPL-2.0，详见 GitHub。</string>
    <string name="info_buttons_body1">A - 短按：NORMAL -> PET -> INFO 循环。</string>
    <string name="info_buttons_body2">A - 短按 - NORMAL 有 prompt：允许一次。</string>
    <string name="info_buttons_body3">A - 长按：开关设备菜单（亮度/声音/重置）。</string>
    <string name="info_buttons_body4">B - 短按 - NORMAL 有 prompt：拒绝。</string>
    <string name="info_buttons_body5">B - 短按 - PET/INFO：翻页。左右滑动亦可。</string>
    <string name="info_credits_body1">Claude 是 Anthropic 的产品，本项目与其无从属关系。</string>
    <string name="info_credits_body2">ASCII 字符源于 @Kenney 的 ASCII pet kit 再创作。</string>
    <string name="info_credits_body3">感谢所有在 issue 区留过反馈的朋友。</string>
